OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy this morning with
OL,6,Fsome showery rain. This afternoon will
OL,7,Fbe dry with some bright or sunny
OL,8,Fspells. Brisk southerly winds across
OL,9,FShetland at first.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be largely
OL,12,Fdry. Clouding over in the early hours
OL,13,Fwith a little rain possible later in
OL,14,Fthe night. Fresh occasionally strong
OL,15,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FShetland rather cloudy at
OL,18,Ffirst with some showery rain.
OL,19,FOtherwise dry with a few sunny spells.
OL,20,FFresh southwesterly winds easing in
OL,21,Fthe afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
