OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry on Tuesday and Wednesday, perhaps
OL,7,Fthe odd shower. Rain spreading east on
OL,8,FThursday, drier later.
